==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Patricide
<hw>Pat*ri"cide</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>pater</ets> father + <ets>caedere</ets> to kill. Cf.
<er>Parricide</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The murderer of his
father.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The crime of one who murders his father. Same as
<er>Parricide</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>patrikin</ent>⟦br⟧
